_sText:
This map has been re-uploaded and should now work Installation: You should have no trouble extracting the contents of the zip to your cstrike folder. (eg steamapps\your-email\counter-strike source\cstrike) Failing that use the folder structure in the zip to see where the files need to go. Map Details: cs_office07 is a 100% re-make of Turtle Rock's cs_office, no copy and pasting - map was built from scratch brush by brush. Author: Simon 'Blink' Smith
You can contact me via this form regarding anything about this map.
